3. Adding a New Package (Step-by-Step Workflow)
Follow these steps whenever you create a new package on your network.

-- --------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Step 1: Create Package in Billing Web GUI
Create your new package (e.g., 20Mbps-JunOS) in the DMA Billing interface. Note the exact spelling.
-- --------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

-- --------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Step 2: Retrieve the Service ID (srvid)
Log into your MariaDB terminal and run the following query to find the auto-generated ID for your package:

USE radius;
SELECT srvid, srvname FROM rm_services WHERE srvname LIKE '%20Mbps%';

