Step 4: Verification
1. Assign the package to your subscriber (e.g., test-user) in the Web Panel.
2. Verify database synchronization:
SELECT * FROM radusergroup WHERE username = 'test-user';
3. Clear the subscriber session on the Juniper BNG CLI:
clear pppoe user test-user
4. Verify active rate limits on the BNG:
run show subscribers username test-user
