4. Troubleshooting & Maintenance
   * Verify Radius Active Attributes (Debug Mode): Run /usr/local/sbin/radiusd -X and check if the Access-Accept packet contains:
ERX-Service-Activate:1 += "svc-internet(15360,15360)"
   * Clean Stuck Accounting Sessions: If a user session hangs in the database, force-close it:
UPDATE radacct SET acctstoptime = NOW(), acctterminatecause = 'Admin-Reset' WHERE username = 'username' AND acctstoptime IS NULL;
